flowchart TD
    A[Exception Caught] --> B{Exception Type?}
    
    B -->|LLMParseError| C[Increment attempt]
    C --> D{attempt < max?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Add error SystemMessage]
    E --> F[Yield RetryEvent]
    F --> G[Retry graph execution]
    D -->|No| H[Yield ErrorEvent]
    
    B -->|ToolExecutionError| I[Increment attempt]
    I --> J{should_retry?}
    J -->|Yes| E
    J -->|No| H
    
    B -->|AgentException| H
    B -->|Other Exception| H
    
    H --> K[End processing]
    G --> A
